{"tid":1429951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日係深水埗走果陣...的士司機咁同我講","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:00:20.000Z","uid":135438,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"383a4d28f186aba59305cfd48bbc8f1d1c17911d","tid":1429951,"uid":135438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"琴日係深水埗發夢夢到夜晚2, 3點果陣搭的士走<br />\n個的士司機見我係深水埗上車，大概都明白我岩岩發完夢，然後佢同我講:<br />\n「你地呀，一定要小心呀，呢兩個月黎我都冇咩心機番工，但我呢兩個月番工賺到既錢都幾乎捐哂幫你地。你地仲後生，我只係希望你地唔好太暴力，因為人地有槍你得把遮，你地係打唔嬴架。」<br />\n到最後個的士司機堅持唔收我錢，仲同我講: 「一定要繼續打落去呀後生仔 !」<br />\n致望緊呢個post既連登仔、中年人、公公婆婆、冇AC既CD-ROM、大愛左翼/左膠，<br />\n我承認抗爭者一定係有D行為係要反省，<br />\n但就算見到佢地做火系魔法師又好，有激進行為都好，<br />\n請唔好諗割席好嘛？<br />\n當全港人唔同界別嘅人都站在抗爭者一方嘅時候，我地一齊合作將個夢發落去好嘛 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd6e761c95ebe2c3e5a4e4c7451e2715c586697","tid":1429951,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"黎到夏慤道呀，帶乜撚野好呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429895</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"937a710400eb8cc45c8680031e37b0043ddde42b","tid":1429951,"uid":135438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a2f2719dc1b46e99b4686f640e5ec74f2bac1f0b","tid":1429951,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6eff34c98183e295ec3c709dbaf07884926e80","tid":1429951,"uid":93908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff579c3ace13ae8cebb63d6d515bb462e2a27c2","tid":1429951,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT